2 - What is Angular 2
Angular 2 is the secong version of Angular JS a Javascript Single Page Application Framework (SPA).
SPA gives desktop like experience within web apps due to the way in which SPA's operate.
There is a definition and detailed explanation of SPA at the following address -
http://singlepageappbook.com/goal.html

